WOMEN'S SHOES

From turning heads to torching your personal best, your shoes do a lot of work. adidas offers womens shoes for every sport and setting to keep you at the top of your game. Find minimalist runners, chunky shoes inspired by 90s aesthetics, iconic silhouettes with canvas or premium leather, womens slides and more.

ATHLETIC SHOES FOR WOMEN

Whether youre trimming seconds off your mile or pushing through a circuit training session, performance-ready athletic shoes are essential to getting the most out of your workout. Hit that runners high before you even head out the door in womens running shoes with ventilated knit uppers and ultra-comfortable Boost cushioning. Training shoes offer lateral support and outsoles with enhanced traction to keep you grounded as you power through high-intensity intervals. Water-repellant womens golf shoes help you stay swinging smoothly no matter the elements.

WOMEN'S CASUAL SHOES & SNEAKERS

Strolling to coffee or stepping into yoga class, your shoes are an opportunity to experience comfort and make a statement. Find iconic womens sneakers like the adidas Superstar with durable leather uppers and its signature shell-toe or womens Stan Smiths with their clean, clublike silhouette and subtle accents. Bring some past into your present with retro-inspired shoes that capture the spirit of 70s runners, 90s cross-trainers and everything in between. On workdays and weekends, slip in classic adidas slides. Womens sandals and slides feature a contour footbed for all-day comfort and a range of colorways to express your style.

HOW TO PREVENT CHAFING

Even the most seasoned runner needs to be prepared for the unknown and the last thing you want after a tough run is chafe. Check out our tips on How to Prevent Chafing to help you stay on the go whether it be on your usual route or running a marathon!
